General.Name: Chander Electronics Corp.
General.Description: Chander Electronics Corp. engages in the distribution, trade, and maintenance of electronic components, integrated circuits, computer equipment, and related products primarily in Taiwan. The company is also involved in the wholesale and retail of tobacco, alcohol, beverage, food, and medical equipment; and investment activities. Chander Electronics Corp. was incorporated in 1997 and is based in New Taipei City, Taiwan.
